creator: Empower Finance
descriptionHtml:
Save, budget, bank and manage your money wisely with a financial expert in your pocket. Join the 650,000+ people who use Empower to master their money, get finance tips and crush their financial goals.

Track money, manage spend and save more with Empower. Why? Because we want you to reach your money goals. Let’s break it down:

Save money with automated saving.
You could save $1,500 or more every year - set a weekly savings target, and reach your financial goals. We’ll track money and spending and bank the right amount of money for you. This is the simple way to achieve your money goals.

- Earn 0.25% APY on savings when you also open an Empower interest checking account
- Empower deposits are FDIC insured up to $250,000*
- Access your money anytime
- No account minimums

Save money with our budgeting and spend tracking.
Banking doesn’t need to be hard. We’ll whip up a budget that reflects your lifestyle. Manage and track money against your bills and purchases so you can work towards your financial goals.

- Customizable budget categories
- Track money with weekly or monthly spend limits
- 24/7 alerts on $ left to spend
- Monthly reports to help you manage your spend

Expert finance tips.
We have human coaches ready to share personalized recommendations and finance tips on how to pay down debt, uncover extra savings, and tackle any other finance issues.

Save money and crush your money goals the easy way! We keep an eye on your money so you don’t have to. It’s like having a personalized banking expert in your pocket. Sit back, relax, and we’ll tell you when and how to make better financial choices. We’ll notify you about these (and more):

- Account alerts – Empower notifies you about banking fees, bill increases, missed bills, credit utilization, new ways to save, and more
- Subscription management – Empower shows you all of your subscriptions and helps you cancel any you're not using anymore.
- Bill negotiation – Empower negotiates your phone, cable and internet bills to get you better deals.

Human coach.
Our human coaches are always here to help you through any financial challenge. Think personalized tips to steer you in the right direction.

Industry-leading interest on checking.
Spend, save, budget - you choose. Our APY is higher than your traditional bank and we’ll help your savings grow to get you closer to your money goals.

- 0.25% APY on all your money
- Debit card with 24/7 alerts on all transactions
- 3 monthly ATM fee reimbursements^
- Empower deposits are FDIC insured up to $250,000*
- No overdraft fees
- No insufficient funds fees
- No account minimums
- Feature to lock/unlock your card in-app

Download Empower today to save money, reach your financial goals and watch your savings grow.

Data privacy and security.
Your personal data belongs to you, and you alone. We would never share or sell your information to another party. And we keep your money safe and sound with the latest-and-greatest bank-grade security features and protections, like:

- AES 256-bit encryption
- Multi-factor authentication
- Touch/Face ID

For more information, visit empower.me.

*Banking services for new accounts provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC. 0.25% Annual Percentage Yield (APY) may change at any time. APY as of May 14, 2020. Empower charges an auto-recurring subscription fee of $6 for access to the full suite of money management features offered on the platform after your first 30 days.

^Empower does not charge foreign transaction fees for the use of the Empower Visa Debit Card outside of the US. However, Visa charges a foreign transaction fee of 1%. Empower does not reimburse this 1% transaction fee on foreign ATM transactions or on any other foreign transactions or purchases. Reimbursement for up to 3 ATM fees per month, with a maximum reimbursement of $10 per ATM withdrawal.

Annual savings through our AutoSave feature may vary based on the customer’s savings selection and financial circumstances.

title: Empower: Cash advance, savings & budget app

creator: Empower Finance
descriptionHtml:
Empower is mobile banking designed for today’s generation. Get an instant cash advance up to $250*. Spend mindfully with no overdraft fees. Build your savings for the future. Budget better with personalizable spending trackers. Because this is what mobile banking should be, a partner that understands you and gets you where you want to go. No matter what lies ahead, we’ll help you thrive.

Empower Cash Advance*: We know you’re doing everything you can to get ahead, but some months it’s just not enough. Empower will float you up to $250 in fast cash advance when you need it most. There’s no interest, no late fees, and no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck. Why rely on predatory payday loans when Empower offers the no-fee cash advance you’ve always wanted.

Empower Interest Checking**: We know it’s tough to find a bank offering a checking account without the sneaky fees and with the flexibility you need. Empower offers instant delivery of your cash advance for life’s little emergencies. There’s no account minimums and no overdraft or insufficient funds fees, plus count on 3 ATM reimbursements every single month^. Your account also comes with an Empower Visa debit card and built-in, easy-to-use, real-time spend trackers to keep your expenses under control. And on top of all that, Empower will pay you 0.25% APY** on all your deposits so you make money daily.

Empower Automated Saving**: We know how hard saving can be, and the trick is to save small amounts continuously — and let a savings app do it for you. Empower automates the process of saving so you never have to lift a finger. Just set a weekly savings target, and we’ll monitor your income and spending to identify the best time to set money aside from your checking account into savings (where you’re less likely to spend it!). It’s called AutoSave — just set it and forget it. And if you open an Empower Interest Checking account, Empower will pay you 0.25% APY** on all your savings. Empower AutoSave is the simplest way to save money.

Empower Subscription Manager: We show you all of your subscriptions and help you cancel any you're not using anymore, so you don’t waste your hard-earned money on subscriptions you no longer need or want.

Empower Alerts: We monitor your money and send proactive notifications about bill increases, missed bills, bank fees, credit utilization, and more, making it easy to stay on top of your finances.

Empower deposits are FDIC insured up to $250,000**.

Privacy: Your personal data belongs to you, and you alone. We would never share or sell your information to another party.

Security: We keep your money safe and sound with the latest-and-greatest bank-grade security features and protections: AES 256-bit encryption, multi-factor authentication, Touch/Face ID.

For more information, visit empower.me.

* Access to the cash advance feature and different cash advance amounts is determined by Empower based on various criteria including bank account history and activity, recurring direct deposits, average monthly direct deposit, repayment history, and other factors. Minimum direct deposits to an Empower checking account, among other conditions, are necessary to qualify for instant delivery and advances greater than $50.

^ Reimbursement for up to 3 ATM fees per month, with a maximum reimbursement of $10 per ATM withdrawal.

** Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC. 0.25% Annual Percentage Yield (APY) may change at any time. APY as of August 12, 2020. Empower charges an auto-recurring subscription fee of $8 for access to the full suite of money management features offered on the platform after your first 30 days.

Empower does not charge foreign transaction fees for the use of the Empower Visa Debit Card outside of the US. However, Visa charges a foreign transaction fee of 1%. Empower does not reimburse this 1% transaction fee on foreign ATM transactions or on any other foreign transactions or purchases.

The Empower Card is the only card you’ll ever need. Score Cash Advance up to $250* with no interest. Get paid up to 2 days faster†. Earn up to 10% cashback^. And never pay another overdraft fee. No matter what lies ahead, we’ll help you thrive.

(Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.)

GET CASH ADVANCE UP TO $250*
You’re doing everything you can to get ahead, but some weeks it’s just not enough. Empower will float you up to $250 in fast cash advance when you need it most — No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

GET PAID UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†
Set up paycheck deposit to Empower, and we’ll make that money available to you ASAP. That means up to 2 days earlier than most banks. Total game changer.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK^
Save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No random offers, only great deals you’re certain to use every week.

GET FREE ATM WITHDRAWALS
Enjoy convenient access to over 37,000 ATM locations across the US. Use them as often as you want, whenever you want, and never get charged a single dime for taking out cash.

GET FAST SERVICE
We’ve got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone, live chat, or email Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT.

Empower also helps you:

TRACK YOUR SPEND
Take control of impulse shopping with 24/7 alerts that monitor your expenses against your spend limits by category.

SAVE AUTOMATICALLY
Set aside cash for emergencies and big purchases — without lifting a finger. Just tell us your weekly savings target, and we’ll study your income and expenses daily to figure out when and how much you can afford to save. We’ll automatically move that money from your spending account to your Empower AutoSave Account so it’s there for you when you need it.

–––––

NO-NONSENSE PRIVACY
Your personal data belongs to you, and you alone. We would never share or sell your information to a third party.

STRICT SECURITY
We keep your money safe and sound with the latest-and-greatest bank-grade security features and protections: AES 256-bit encryption, multi-factor authentication, Touch/Face ID.

For more information, visit empower.me.

–––––

* Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card. Cash Advances can be repaid at any time after the advance is taken. If no payment is made prior to the agreed upon repayment date, Empower will initiate an electronic debit on the agreed upon due date, and if balance is not paid in full, Empower will attempt to debit until repayment is made in accordance with our Terms and Conditions and Cash Advance Authorization.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds depends on the timing of the employer's submission of deposits. We generally post such deposits on the day they are received which may be up to 2 days earlier than the employer's scheduled payment date.

^ Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases, including categories, merchants, and percentages, will vary and must be selected in the app. Cashback will be applied automatically when the final transaction posts, which may be up to a week after the qualifying purchase.

Empower charges an auto-recurring monthly subscription fee of $8 for access to the full suite of money management features offered on the platform. The subscription fee will apply (a) after the 14-day free trial concludes for first-time customers, and (b) immediately for customers returning for a second or subsequent subscription. Empower deposits are FDIC insured up to $250,000.

Empower does not charge foreign transaction fees for the use of the Empower Visa Debit Card outside of the US. However, Visa charges a foreign transaction fee of 1%. Empower does not reimburse this 1% transaction fee on foreign ATM transactions or on any other foreign transactions or purchases.

The Empower Card is the only card you’ll ever need. Score Cash Advance up to $250* with no interest. Get paid up to 2 days faster†. Earn up to 10% cashback^. And never pay another overdraft fee. No matter what lies ahead, we’ll help you thrive.

(Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.)

GET CASH ADVANCE UP TO $250*
You’re doing everything you can to get ahead, but some weeks it’s just not enough. Empower will float you up to $250 in fast cash advance when you need it most — No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

GET PAID UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†
Set up paycheck deposit to Empower, and we’ll make that money available to you ASAP. That means up to 2 days earlier than most banks. Total game changer.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK^
Save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No random offers, only great deals you’re certain to use every week.

GET FREE ATM WITHDRAWALS
Enjoy convenient access to over 37,000 ATM locations across the US. Use them as often as you want, whenever you want, and never get charged a single dime for taking out cash.

GET FAST SERVICE
We’ve got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone, live chat, or email Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT.

Empower also helps you:

TRACK YOUR SPEND
Take control of impulse shopping with 24/7 alerts that monitor your expenses against your spend limits by category.

SAVE AUTOMATICALLY
Set aside cash for emergencies and big purchases — without lifting a finger. Just tell us your weekly savings target, and we’ll study your income and expenses daily to figure out when and how much you can afford to save. We’ll automatically move that money from your spending account to your Empower AutoSave Account so it’s there for you when you need it.

–––––

NO-NONSENSE PRIVACY
Your personal data belongs to you, and you alone. We would never share or sell your information to a third party.

STRICT SECURITY
We keep your money safe and sound with the latest-and-greatest bank-grade security features and protections: AES 256-bit encryption, multi-factor authentication, Touch/Face ID.

For more information, visit empower.me.

–––––

* Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card. Cash Advances can be repaid at any time after the advance is taken. If no payment is made prior to the agreed upon repayment date, Empower will initiate an electronic debit on the agreed upon due date, and if balance is not paid in full, Empower will attempt to debit until repayment is made in accordance with our Terms and Conditions and Cash Advance Authorization.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds depends on the timing of the employer's submission of deposits. We generally post such deposits on the day they are received which may be up to 2 days earlier than the employer's scheduled payment date.

^ Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases, including categories, merchants, and percentages, will vary and must be selected in the app. Cashback will be applied automatically when the final transaction posts, which may be up to a week after the qualifying purchase.

Empower charges an auto-recurring monthly subscription fee of $8 for access to the full suite of money management features offered on the platform. The subscription fee will apply (a) after the 14-day free trial concludes for first-time customers, and (b) immediately for customers returning for a second or subsequent subscription. Empower deposits are FDIC insured up to $250,000.

Empower does not charge foreign transaction fees for the use of the Empower Visa Debit Card outside of the US. However, Visa charges a foreign transaction fee of 1%. Empower does not reimburse this 1% transaction fee on foreign ATM transactions or on any other foreign transactions or purchases.

title: Empower: Instant Cash Advance. Get up to $250.

creator: Empower Finance
descriptionHtml:
Think the credit system is stacked against you? So do we. Empower is on a mission to help more people access affordable credit, build their credit history, and rewrite their financial story. No credit score or security deposit to qualify.

(Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC. Empower Thrive provided by FinWise Bank, Member FDIC.)

GET CASH ADVANCE UP TO $250*
Tight on cash and tired of asking friends to cover you? Empower will float you anywhere from $25 to $250 when you need it most. Instant delivery available. No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

BUILD UP TO $1,000 OVER TIME WITH AN EMPOWER REVOLVING THRIVE LINE OF CREDIT^ (COMING SOON!)
Start with a $200 revolving line of credit and grow to $1,000 with every on-time payment. Enjoy instant delivery and 0% APR** (when you pay your balance on your next paycheck date, otherwise 36% APR). Building credit just got a whole lot easier.

GET YOUR PAYCHECK UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†
Wish payday came sooner? Wish no more. With the Empower Card, you can get paid up to 2 days earlier than most banks.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK†
Perks of a credit card but with a debit card. With the Empower Card, save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No overdraft fees.

GET FREE ATM WITHDRAWALS
Enjoy convenient access with the Empower Card to over 37,000 MoneyPass ATMs across the US. Use them as often as you want, whenever you want, and never get charged a single dime for taking out cash.

GET FAST SERVICE
We’ve got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone or live chat Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT. (We’ve got email too if that’s more your jam.)

TRACK YOUR SPEND
Take control of your finances by monitoring your spend against weekly or monthly category limits. We’ll send you 24/7 alerts to help you do better.

–

Empower charges an auto-recurring monthly subscription fee of $8 (a) after the 14-day free trial concludes for first-time customers, and (b) immediately for customers returning for a second or subsequent subscription. Cancel anytime.

* Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card.

^ Eligibility requirements apply. Opening an Empower Thrive line of credit restricts access to Empower Cash Advance, with access restricted until the Empower Thrive line of credit is closed and you meet the eligibility requirements for Empower Cash Advance. Instant delivery is available for a 5% fee of the draw amount on the line of credit. We report your payments to the credit bureaus. Pay on time and keep utilization low for the best potential benefit. Many factors impact your credit score, and while making on-time payments and keeping utilization low may improve your score, there is no guarantee this will improve your score.

** The Annual Percentage Rate is subject to change. An Empower Thrive line of credit is subject to credit approval. There are no costs to open an Empower Thrive line of credit. If you choose to pay your draw in full on your next paycheck date, your rate will be 0% APR; if you miss your payment, you will accrue interest at 36% APR and may incur late fees. If you choose to pay your draw on a date other than your next paycheck date, your rate will be 36% APR or as otherwise required by state law.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds depends on the timing of the employer's submission of deposits. We generally post such deposits on the day they are received which may be up to 2 days earlier than the employer's scheduled payment date. Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases, including categories, merchants, and percentages, will vary and must be selected in the app. Cashback will be applied automatically when the final transaction posts, which may be up to a week after the qualifying purchase.

descriptionHtml:
"The Empower Card is the only card you'll ever need. Score Cash Advance up to $250* with no interest. Get paid up to 2 days faster†. Earn up to 10% cashback^. And never pay another overdraft fee. No matter what lies ahead, we'll help you thrive. (Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.)

GET CASH ADVANCE UP TO $250* You're doing everything you can to get ahead, but some weeks it's just not enough. Empower will float you up to $250 in fast cash advance when you need it most — No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

GET PAID UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER† Set up paycheck deposit to Empower, and we'll make that money available to you ASAP. That means up to 2 days earlier than most banks. Total game changer.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK^ Save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No random offers, only great deals you're certain to use every week.

GET FREE ATM WITHDRAWALS Enjoy convenient access to over 37,000 ATM locations across the US. Use them as often as you want, whenever you want, and never get charged a single dime for taking out cash.

GET FAST SERVICE We've got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone, live chat, or email Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT.

Empower also helps you: TRACK YOUR SPEND Take control of impulse shopping with 24/7 alerts that monitor your expenses against your spend limits by category. SAVE AUTOMATICALLY Set aside cash for emergencies and big purchases — without lifting a finger. Just tell us your weekly savings target, and we'll study your income and expenses daily to figure out when and how much you can afford to save. We'll automatically move that money from your spending account to your Empower AutoSave Account so it's there for you when you need it. ––––– NO-NONSENSE PRIVACY Your personal data belongs to you, and you alone. We would never share or sell your information to a third party. STRICT SECURITY We keep your money safe and sound with the latest-and-greatest bank-grade security features and protections: AES 256-bit encryption, multi-factor authentication, Touch/Face ID. For more information, visit empower.me. ––––– * Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card. No mandatory minimum or maximum repayment timeframe. Repay us when you get paid or when you can afford it.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds depends on the timing of the employer's submission of deposits. We generally post such deposits on the day they are received which may be up to 2 days earlier than the employer's scheduled payment date. ^ Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases, including categories, merchants, and percentages, will vary and must be selected in the app. Cashback will be applied automatically when the final transaction posts, which may be up to a week after the qualifying purchase. The subscription fee will apply (a) after the 14-day free trial concludes for first-time customers, and (b) immediately for customers returning for a second or subsequent subscription. Empower deposits are FDIC insured up to $250,000. Empower does not charge foreign transaction fees for the use of the Empower Visa Debit Card outside of the US. However, Visa charges a foreign transaction fee of 1%. Empower does not reimburse this 1% transaction fee on foreign ATM transactions or on any other foreign transactions or purchases.' for the locale English (United States)"

descriptionHtml:
The Empower Card is the only card you'll ever need. Score Cash Advance up to $250* with no interest. Get paid up to 2 days faster†. Earn up to 10% cashback^. And never pay another overdraft fee. No matter what lies ahead, we'll help you thrive.

(Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.)

GET CASH ADVANCE UP TO $250*. You're doing everything you can to get ahead, but some weeks it's just not enough. Empower will float you up to $250 in fast cash advance when you need it most — No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

GET PAID UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†. Set up paycheck deposit to Empower, and we'll make that money available to you ASAP. That means up to 2 days earlier than most banks. Total game changer.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK^. Save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No random offers, only great deals you're certain to use every week.

GET FREE ATM WITHDRAWALS. Enjoy convenient access to over 37,000 ATM locations across the US. Use them as often as you want, whenever you want, and never get charged a single dime for taking out cash.

GET FAST SERVICE. We've got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone, live chat, or email Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT.

Empower also helps you:

TRACK YOUR SPEND. Take control of impulse shopping with 24/7 alerts that monitor your expenses against your spend limits by category.

SAVE AUTOMATICALLY. Set aside cash for emergencies and big purchases — without lifting a finger. Just tell us your weekly savings target, and we'll study your income and expenses daily to figure out when and how much you can afford to save. We'll automatically move that money from your spending account to your Empower AutoSave Account so it's there for you when you need it.

–––––

NO-NONSENSE PRIVACY. Your personal data belongs to you, and you alone. We would never share or sell your information to a third party.

STRICT SECURITY. We keep your money safe and sound with the latest-and-greatest bank-grade security features and protections: AES 256-bit encryption, multi-factor authentication, Touch/Face ID. For more information, visit empower.me.

–––––

* Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card. No mandatory minimum or maximum repayment timeframe. Repay us when you get paid or when you can afford it.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds depends on the timing of the employer's submission of deposits. We generally post such deposits on the day they are received which may be up to 2 days earlier than the employer's scheduled payment date.

^ Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases, including categories, merchants, and percentages, will vary and must be selected in the app. Cashback will be applied automatically when the final transaction posts, which may be up to a week after the qualifying purchase.

Empower charges an auto-recurring monthly subscription fee of $8 for access to the full suite of money management features offered on the platform. The subscription fee will apply (a) after the 14-day free trial concludes for first-time customers, and (b) immediately for customers returning for a second or subsequent subscription. Empower deposits are FDIC insured up to $250,000. Empower does not charge foreign transaction fees for the use of the Empower Visa Debit Card outside of the US. However, Visa charges a foreign transaction fee of 1%. Empower does not reimburse this 1% transaction fee on foreign ATM transactions or on any other foreign transactions or purchases.

BUILD UP TO $1,000 OVER TIME WITH AN EMPOWER THRIVE REVOLVING LINE OF CREDIT^ (COMING SOON!)
Start with a $200 revolving line of credit and grow to $1,000 with every on-time payment. Enjoy instant delivery and 0% APR** (when you pay your balance on your next paycheck date, otherwise 35.99% APR). Building credit just got a whole lot easier.

GET YOUR PAYCHECK UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†
Wish payday came sooner? Wish no more. With the Empower Card, you can get paid up to 2 days earlier than most banks.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK†
Perks of a credit card but with a debit card. With the Empower Card, save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No overdraft fees.

–

* Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card.

^ Eligibility requirements apply. Opening an Empower Thrive line of credit restricts access to Empower Cash Advance, with access restricted until the Empower Thrive line of credit is closed and you meet the eligibility requirements for Empower Cash Advance. Instant delivery is available for a 5% fee of the draw amount on the line of credit. We report your payments to the credit bureaus. Pay on time and keep utilization low for the best potential benefit. Many factors impact your credit score, and while making on-time payments and keeping utilization low may improve your score, there is no guarantee this will improve your score.

** The Annual Percentage Rate is subject to change. An Empower Thrive line of credit is subject to credit approval. There are no costs to open an Empower Thrive line of credit. If you choose to pay your draw in full on your next paycheck date, your rate will be 0% APR; if you miss your payment, you will accrue interest at 35.99% APR and may incur late fees. If you choose to pay your draw on a date other than your next paycheck date, your rate will be 35.99% APR or as otherwise required by state law.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds may vary by employer. Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases will vary and must be selected in the app.

descriptionHtml:
The Empower Card is the only card you'll ever need. Score Cash Advance up to $250* with no interest. Get paid up to 2 days faster†. Earn up to 10% cashback^. And never pay another overdraft fee. No matter what lies ahead, we'll help you thrive.

(Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.)

GET CASH ADVANCE UP TO $250*. You're doing everything you can to get ahead, but some weeks it's just not enough. Empower will float you up to $250 in fast cash advance when you need it most — No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

GET PAID UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†. Set up paycheck deposit to Empower, and we'll make that money available to you ASAP. That means up to 2 days earlier than most banks. Total game changer.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK^. Save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No random offers, only great deals you're certain to use every week.

GET FREE ATM WITHDRAWALS. Enjoy convenient access to over 37,000 ATM locations across the US. Use them as often as you want, whenever you want, and never get charged a single dime for taking out cash.

GET FAST SERVICE. We've got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone, live chat, or email Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT.

Empower also helps you:

TRACK YOUR SPEND. Take control of impulse shopping with 24/7 alerts that monitor your expenses against your spend limits by category.

SAVE AUTOMATICALLY. Set aside cash for emergencies and big purchases — without lifting a finger. Just tell us your weekly savings target, and we'll study your income and expenses daily to figure out when and how much you can afford to save. We'll automatically move that money from your spending account to your Empower AutoSave Account so it's there for you when you need it.

–––––

NO-NONSENSE PRIVACY. Your personal data belongs to you, and you alone. We would never share or sell your information to a third party.

STRICT SECURITY. We keep your money safe and sound with the latest-and-greatest bank-grade security features and protections: AES 256-bit encryption, multi-factor authentication, Touch/Face ID. For more information, visit empower.me.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Hey there, how are you doing? Like, really doing? May is Mental Health Awareness Month and we know finances can cause a lot of stress which directly impacts your mental health. We created Empower to help alleviate some of that pressure and give you a helping hand when you need it most. So, be sure to take care of yourself and we’re here if you need us. Oh, and we should probably mention this update fixes a few bugs to improve your overall experience.

descriptionShort: Cash Advance with no interest or late fees.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: It’s a new month and Summer is officially here. This might be one of the toughest summers yet, with rising gas prices, inflation and not to mention Starbucks raising their prices. It’s hard to see the light at the end of the tunnel. But just a reminder that we’ll always be here when you need extra cash to help you get by. Hang in there, friends. Oh and this update with fix some bugs and things. Now goodbye for real. At least until the next update.

BUILD UP TO $1,000 OVER TIME WITH AN EMPOWER THRIVE REVOLVING LINE OF CREDIT^ (COMING SOON!)
Start with a $200 revolving line of credit and grow to $1,000 with every on-time payment. Enjoy instant delivery and 0% APR** (when you pay your balance on your next paycheck date, otherwise 35.99% APR). Building credit just got a whole lot easier.

GET YOUR PAYCHECK UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†
Wish payday came sooner? Wish no more. With the Empower Card, you can get paid up to 2 days earlier than most banks.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK†
Perks of a credit card but with a debit card. With the Empower Card, save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No overdraft fees.

–

descriptionShort: Cash Advance with no interest or late fees.
title: Empower: Instant Cash Advance.

creator: Empower Finance
descriptionHtml:
The Empower Card is the only card you'll ever need. Score Cash Advance up to $250* with no interest. Get paid up to 2 days faster†. Earn up to 10% cashback^. And never pay another overdraft fee. No matter what lies ahead, we'll help you thrive.

(Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.)

GET CASH ADVANCE UP TO $250*. You're doing everything you can to get ahead, but some weeks it's just not enough. Empower will float you up to $250 in fast cash advance when you need it most — No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

GET PAID UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†. Set up paycheck deposit to Empower, and we'll make that money available to you ASAP. That means up to 2 days earlier than most banks. Total game changer.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK^. Save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No random offers, only great deals you're certain to use every week.

GET FREE ATM WITHDRAWALS. Enjoy convenient access to over 37,000 ATM locations across the US. Use them as often as you want, whenever you want, and never get charged a single dime for taking out cash.

GET FAST SERVICE. We've got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone, live chat, or email Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT.

Empower also helps you:

TRACK YOUR SPEND. Take control of impulse shopping with 24/7 alerts that monitor your expenses against your spend limits by category.

SAVE AUTOMATICALLY. Set aside cash for emergencies and big purchases — without lifting a finger. Just tell us your weekly savings target, and we'll study your income and expenses daily to figure out when and how much you can afford to save. We'll automatically move that money from your spending account to your Empower AutoSave Account so it's there for you when you need it.

–––––

NO-NONSENSE PRIVACY. Your personal data belongs to you, and you alone. We would never share or sell your information to a third party.

STRICT SECURITY. We keep your money safe and sound with the latest-and-greatest bank-grade security features and protections: AES 256-bit encryption, multi-factor authentication, Touch/Face ID. For more information, visit empower.me.

–––––

* Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card. No mandatory minimum or maximum repayment timeframe. Repay us when you get paid or when you can afford it.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds depends on the timing of the employer's submission of deposits. We generally post such deposits on the day they are received which may be up to 2 days earlier than the employer's scheduled payment date.

^ Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases, including categories, merchants, and percentages, will vary and must be selected in the app. Cashback will be applied automatically when the final transaction posts, which may be up to a week after the qualifying purchase.

Empower charges an auto-recurring monthly subscription fee of $8 for access to the full suite of money management features offered on the platform. The subscription fee will apply (a) after the 14-day free trial concludes for first-time customers, and (b) immediately for customers returning for a second or subsequent subscription. Empower deposits are FDIC insured up to $250,000. Empower does not charge foreign transaction fees for the use of the Empower Visa Debit Card outside of the US. However, Visa charges a foreign transaction fee of 1%. Empower does not reimburse this 1% transaction fee on foreign ATM transactions or on any other foreign transactions or purchases.

GET YOUR PAYCHECK UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†
Wish payday came sooner? Wish no more. With the Empower Card, you can get paid up to 2 days earlier than most banks.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK†
Perks of a credit card but with a debit card. With the Empower Card, save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more. No overdraft fees.

GET FREE ATM WITHDRAWALS
Enjoy convenient access with the Empower Card to over 37,000 MoneyPass ATMs across the US. Use them as often as you want, whenever you want, and never get charged a single dime for taking out cash.

Take control of your finances by monitoring your spend against weekly or monthly limits by category. We’ll send you 24/7 alerts to coach you on how to do better.

descriptionShort: Cash Advance with no interest or late fees.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: NO-vember is here and you know what that means! Saying no to things that aren’t in our budget, so we can save that bread. Treat this month as an investment in yourself— saving up for things you need or maybe even want. You got this. Oh and we fixed a few bugs and other things so the app is ready for this big challenge. Good luck!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Thanksgiving is a time to be grateful for what you already have. Now keep this same energy when Black Friday ads start hitting your inbox. We’re not here to encourage excessive spending but we’re also not here to judge. If you find yourself in a financial pickle, we’ve got your back. Wishing you a very happy holiday and we hope it’s one to remember. Oh, we made an update to fix a few bugs and things. Now please enjoy some pie for the both of us.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: How are we already halfway through August?! Well, now is the perfect time to get your finances back on track. title: Empower: Instant Cash Advance.

creator: Empower Finance
descriptionHtml:
Need extra cash to make it to your next paycheck? Empower’s got your back. Get up to $250 instantly*. Say goodbye to overdraft fees and stressing about money. No credit score or security deposit to qualify.

(Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.)

GET INSTANT CASH UP TO $250*
Tight on cash and tired of asking friends to cover you? Empower will float you up to $250 when you need it most. Instant delivery available. No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

Empower Cash Advance is NOT a personal loan:
— Repay on your next paycheck or change to when best. There is no minimum or maximum timeline for repayment.
— No interest (0% APR)
— Example: If you accept a $50 instant Cash Advance to your external account for a $3 instant delivery fee, then your total repayment amount will be $53.

STAY TUNED FOR EMPOWER THRIVE (COMING SOON)^
Get the money you need. Build the credit you want.

PUT AWAY MONEY FOR BILLS WITH AUTOMATIC SAVINGS
Avoid spending the money you need for bills by putting it away with AutoSave. With AutoSave you decide how much to save and when. Once your bill is due, withdraw the money from your AutoSave account and pay your bill on time.

GET YOUR PAYCHECK UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†
Wish your paycheck came sooner? Wish no more. With the Empower Card account, you can get paid up to 2 days earlier than with most banks.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK†
Perks of a credit card but with a debit card. With the Empower Card, save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more.

BUDGET BETTER
Take control of your finances by monitoring your purchases against weekly or monthly limits by category. We’ll send you 24/7 alerts to coach you on how to do better.

GET FAST SERVICE
We’ve got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone or live chat Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT. (We’ve got email too if that’s more your jam.)

–

Empower charges an auto-recurring monthly subscription fee of $8 (a) after the 14-day free trial concludes for first-time customers, and (b) immediately for customers returning for a second or subsequent subscription. Cancel anytime.

* Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card.

^ Empower Thrive provided by FinWise Bank, Member FDIC. The Empower Thrive line of credit is subject to credit approval. Access requires Empower membership of $8 per month.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds may vary by employer. Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases will vary and must be selected in the app.

Need extra cash to make it to your next paycheck? Empower’s got your back. Get up to $250 instantly*. Say goodbye to overdraft fees and stressing about money. No credit score or security deposit to qualify.

(Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.)

GET INSTANT CASH UP TO $250*
Tight on cash and tired of asking friends to cover you? Empower will float you up to $250 when you need it most. Instant delivery available. No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

Empower Cash Advance is NOT a personal loan:
— Repay on your next paycheck or change to when best. There is no minimum or maximum timeline for repayment.
— No interest (0% APR)
— Example: If you accept a $50 instant Cash Advance to your external account for a $3 instant delivery fee, then your total repayment amount will be $53.

STAY TUNED FOR EMPOWER THRIVE (COMING SOON)^
Get the money you need. Build the credit you want.

PUT AWAY MONEY FOR BILLS WITH AUTOMATIC SAVINGS
Avoid spending the money you need for bills by putting it away with AutoSave. With AutoSave you decide how much to save and when. Once your bill is due, withdraw the money from your AutoSave account and pay your bill on time.

GET YOUR PAYCHECK UP TO 2 DAYS FASTER†
Wish your paycheck came sooner? Wish no more. With the Empower Card account, you can get paid up to 2 days earlier than with most banks.

GET UP TO 10% CASHBACK†
Perks of a credit card but with a debit card. With the Empower Card, save money on the places where you shop already, like restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, and more.

BUDGET BETTER
Take control of your finances by monitoring your purchases against weekly or monthly limits by category. We’ll send you 24/7 alerts to coach you on how to do better.

GET FAST SERVICE
We’ve got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone or live chat Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT. (We’ve got email too if that’s more your jam.)

–

Empower charges an auto-recurring monthly subscription fee of $8 (a) after the 14-day free trial concludes for first-time customers, and (b) immediately for customers returning for a second or subsequent subscription. Cancel anytime.

* Eligibility requirements apply. Free instant delivery is available for eligible customers with an activated Empower Card.

^ Empower Thrive provided by FinWise Bank, Member FDIC. The Empower Thrive line of credit is subject to credit approval. Access requires Empower membership of $8 per month.

† Early access to paycheck deposit funds may vary by employer. Cashback deals on Empower Card purchases will vary and must be selected in the app.
descriptionShort: Cash Advance with no interest or late fees.

title:
Empower: Instant Cash Advance.
5.90.0.546

creator: Empower Finance
descriptionHtml:
Need extra cash to make it to your next paycheck? Empower’s got your back. Get $10 to $250 instantly.* Say goodbye to overdraft fees and stressing about money. No credit score or security deposit to qualify.


GET INSTANT CASH FROM $10 TO $250*
Tight on cash and tired of asking friends to cover you? Empower will float you anywhere from $10 to $250 when you need it most. Instant delivery available. No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

Empower Cash Advance is NOT a personal loan:
— No mandatory minimum or maximum repayment timeframe
— No interest (0% APR)
— Example: If you accept a $50 instant Cash Advance to your external account for a $3 instant delivery fee, then your total repayment amount will be $53.

BUILD BETTER CREDIT HISTORY WITH THRIVE^
Credit score holding you back? Empower Thrive is the chance you’ve been waiting for. A flexible line of credit that helps you build the credit history you need to reach those big financial goals. All credit scores welcome and no money down.

— $250 initial credit limit
— Repay it your way
— Enjoy limit increases up to $1,000 over time**
— Build good credit history^

START SAVING FOR THE FUTURE WITH AUTOMATIC SAVINGS
Make investing in your future easier than ever with AutoSave. After you set your savings goal, Empower will monitor your income and spending habits to know when and how much you can afford to save. All you have to do is sit back and watch your savings grow.


KEEP TABS ON YOUR CREDIT SCORE
Watch your hard work pay off by monitoring your credit score. We’ll give you monthly score updates and helpful tips to improve your score. Credit scores are already complicated enough. Let us help you understand it.

GET FAST SERVICE
We’ve got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone or live chat Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT. (We’ve got email too if that’s more your jam.)

–
Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.

Empower offers a 14-day trial for first-time customers only. Once the trial concludes, Empower charges an auto-recurring $8/month subscription fee. If you do not wish to pay the subscription fee, you must cancel your subscription before the end of your trial. If you are a returning customer, you will be charged the $8 fee immediately upon resubscribing. Cancel any time by visiting “Billing” in the mobile app or contacting help@empower.me.

* Not everyone will qualify for a Cash Advance offer. Offer amounts range from $10 - $250. As of 11/30/2023, the average offer amount is $140. Instant delivery is optional, and fees may apply. See Empower’s Terms for instant delivery fee amounts.


^ Empower Thrive provided by FinWise Bank, Member FDIC. The Empower Thrive line of credit is subject to credit approval. We report your payments to the credit bureaus. Failure to make on-time payments may result in negative reporting. Instant delivery is optional, and fees may apply.


**To be eligible for a credit limit increase, you must successfully pay at least your minimum payment by the due date.
descriptionShort: Get Cash Advance instantly, build better credit, track credit score, save money

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Ready to get the credit you deserve? Introducing the new Empower Thrive line of credit. A $250 credit limit that can grow up to $1,000 over time. It has flexible payment plans so you can repay your way to help you build good credit history. Learn more in the app today. Oh, and with all the exciting news we almost forgot to mention we updated the app to fix a few bugs and things.

creator: Empower Finance
descriptionHtml:
Need extra cash to make it to your next paycheck? Empower’s got your back. Get $10 to $250 instantly.* Say goodbye to overdraft fees and stressing about money. No credit score or security deposit to qualify.


GET INSTANT CASH FROM $10 TO $250*
Tight on cash and tired of asking friends to cover you? Empower will float you anywhere from $10 to $250 when you need it most. Instant delivery available. No interest, no late fees, no credit checks. Just pay us back when you get your next paycheck.

Empower Cash Advance is NOT a personal loan:
— No mandatory minimum or maximum repayment timeframe
— No interest (0% APR)
— Example: If you accept a $50 instant Cash Advance to your external account for a $3 instant delivery fee, then your total repayment amount will be $53.

BUILD BETTER CREDIT HISTORY WITH THRIVE^
Credit score holding you back? Empower Thrive is the chance you’ve been waiting for. A flexible line of credit that helps you build the credit history you need to reach those big financial goals. All credit scores welcome and no money down.

— $250 initial credit limit
— Repay it your way
— Enjoy limit increases up to $1,000 over time**
— Build good credit history^

START SAVING FOR THE FUTURE WITH AUTOMATIC SAVINGS
Make investing in your future easier than ever with AutoSave. After you set your savings goal, Empower will monitor your income and spending habits to know when and how much you can afford to save. All you have to do is sit back and watch your savings grow.


KEEP TABS ON YOUR CREDIT SCORE
Watch your hard work pay off by monitoring your credit score. We’ll give you monthly score updates and helpful tips to improve your score. Credit scores are already complicated enough. Let us help you understand it.

GET FAST SERVICE
We’ve got our A team on standby to handle your questions over the phone or live chat Monday-Friday from 6 AM – 6 PM PT. (We’ve got email too if that’s more your jam.)

–
Empower is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services provided by nbkc bank, Member FDIC.

Empower offers a 14-day trial for first-time customers only. Once the trial concludes, Empower charges an auto-recurring $8/month subscription fee. If you do not wish to pay the subscription fee, you must cancel your subscription before the end of your trial. If you are a returning customer, you will be charged the $8 fee immediately upon resubscribing. Cancel any time by visiting “Billing” in the mobile app or contacting help@empower.me.

* Not everyone will qualify for a Cash Advance offer. Offer amounts range from $10 - $250. As of 11/30/2023, the average offer amount is $140. Instant delivery is optional, and fees may apply. See Empower’s Terms for instant delivery fee amounts.


^ Empower Thrive provided by FinWise Bank, Member FDIC. The Empower Thrive line of credit is subject to credit approval. We report your payments to the credit bureaus. Failure to make on-time payments may result in negative reporting. Instant delivery is optional, and fees may apply.


**To be eligible for a credit limit increase, you must successfully pay at least your minimum payment by the due date.
